      <div class="history" >
        <h1 id="hist">History</h1>
        <div class="historySec1">
          <p>In the summer of 2010, Aakash Sharma, a young and visionary medical student, witnessed a heart-wrenching incident that would change his life forever. During his internship at a bustling urban hospital, a critically ill child lost his battle simply because a compatible blood donor couldn't be found in time. Deeply moved and driven by a sense of urgency, Aakash realized the dire need for a more efficient and accessible blood donation system.</p>
          <img src="/images/home2.jpg" alt="Our first successful donation">
        </div>
        <div class="historySec2">
          <img src="/images/home1.jpeg" alt="The first donation center established by Lifespring blood bank">
          <p>With unwavering determination, he founded Lifespring Blood Bank in 2012, envisioning a future where no life would be lost due to a lack of blood. Through tireless efforts and innovative thinking, Lifespring rapidly grew, establishing a vast network of hospitals, donation centers, and transfusion facilities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="historySec3">
          <p>Today, it stands as a beacon of hope, connecting patients and donors seamlessly, and embodying Aakash's dream of saving lives through unity and compassion.</p>
          <img src="/images/home3.jpeg" alt="State of the art equipment in all centers">
        </div>
